sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / kubectl
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Controller as odh-model-controller<br/>8081/TCP Health
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant SM as ServiceMonitor
    participant MetricsSvc as Metrics Service
    participant Client as External Client

    Note over User,Client: Flow 1: InferenceService Deployment

    User->>K8sAPI: POST InferenceService<br/>Auth: User Token, TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event (InferenceService)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Route<br/>Auth: SA Token, TLS 1.2+
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMonitor<br/>Auth: SA Token, TLS 1.2+
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Metrics Service<br/>Auth: SA Token, TLS 1.2+
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ClusterRoleBinding<br/>Auth: SA Token, TLS 1.2+
    Client->>Route: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>TLS (Edge/Re-encrypt)

    Note over User,Client: Flow 2: NIM Account Reconciliation

    participant NGC as NVIDIA NGC API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant NVCR as nvcr.io Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    User->>K8sAPI: POST Account (nim.opendatahub.io)<br/>Auth: User Token, TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event (Account)<br/>Auth: SA Token
    Controller->>NGC: POST /v2/nvcf/validate (validate API key)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token, TLS 1.2+
    NGC-->>Controller: Validation result
    Controller->>NGC: GET /v2/nvcf/models (fetch catalog)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token, TLS 1.2+
    NGC-->>Controller: Model metadata
    Controller->>NVCR: HEAD manifest (verify images)<br/>Auth: Docker $oauthtoken, TLS 1.2+
    NVCR-->>Controller: Manifest response
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ConfigMap (NIM models)<br/>Auth: SA Token, TLS 1.2+
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Template (ServingRuntime)<br/>Auth: SA Token, TLS 1.2+
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Secret (pull secret)<br/>Auth: SA Token, TLS 1.2+

    Note over User,Client: Flow 3: Gateway Discovery (Dashboard)

    participant Dashboard as RHOAI Dashboard
    participant API as model-serving-api<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS

    Dashboard->>API: GET /api/v1/gateways?namespace=ns<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (user JWT)<br/>TLS 1.2+ (FIPS ciphers)
    API->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview<br/>Auth: User Token (impersonated), TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>API: AccessReview result
    API->>K8sAPI: List Gateways (label-filtered)<br/>Auth: SA Token, TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>API: Gateway list
    API-->>Dashboard: JSON [{gateway refs}]

    Note over User,Client: Flow 4: LLM Gateway Auth Bootstrap

    participant LLMISVC as LLMInferenceService
    participant GWR as GatewayReconciler
    participant LLMR as LLMISVCReconciler

    LLMISVC->>GWR: Watch event (gateway ref changed)
    GWR->>K8sAPI: Create EnvoyFilter (TLS filter for Authorino)<br/>Auth: SA Token, TLS 1.2+
    GWR->>K8sAPI: Create AuthPolicy (Gateway-level)<br/>Auth: SA Token, TLS 1.2+
    LLMR->>K8sAPI: Create AuthPolicy (HTTPRoute-level)<br/>Auth: SA Token, TLS 1.2+
